name: Tesla's Love Child
description:
Meanwhile.
Somewhere in London.
In a basement flat several floors beneath Piccadilly, Jemima worked on her latest engineering.
It sounded just as she had hoped.
Smooth and refined.
It didn't clink and didn't chug.
The next move would be to transport her trusty friend.
There was only few she trusted with this mission and she knew exactly who to call.
